mixin App-about-us()
    section.app-about-us
        .container
            h2.app-about-us__title.reveal-zoom Who We Are at PokerProTour
                span.hidden stake app
            ul.app-about-us__items
                li.app-about-us__item.reveal-left
                    h3 Our expertise in poker
                    p With years of experience in the poker community, PokerProTour has become a trusted platform for players worldwide. We provide an immersive and dynamic experience, offering everything from competitive tournaments to casual play.

                li.app-about-us__item.reveal-zoom
                    h3 Cutting-edge technology
                    p At PokerProTour, we leverage the latest in gaming technology to ensure the best possible performance for our users. Our app is optimized for all devices, providing seamless gameplay and engaging features for players of all levels.

                li.app-about-us__item.reveal-left
                    h3 Commitment to our community
                    p We believe in building a strong and vibrant community of poker players. Whether you're competing or just having fun, PokerProTour is designed to bring players together, offering a platform that is welcoming, inclusive, and supportive.

                li.app-about-us__item.reveal-right
                    h3 Our mission and vision
                    p PokerProTour is driven by a passion for poker and the thrill of competition. Our mission is to make poker accessible, fun, and rewarding for everyone, while pushing the boundaries of digital poker experiences for years to come.

            +Link({
                class: 'btn pulse-btn',
                href: '/downlaod/',
                text: 'Join PokerProTour Now',
            })
